01:11:55,779 --> 01:11:59,881
♪

812
01:12:04,153 --> 01:12:07,922
(sobbing)

813
01:13:21,897 --> 01:13:24,999
It's over, Mona.

814
01:13:57,266 --> 01:13:59,000
Excuse me, you
have a cell phone?

815
01:13:59,002 --> 01:14:00,535
Yes.

816
01:14:03,472 --> 01:14:06,040
Can I bring it
back to you?

817
01:14:06,042 --> 01:14:07,675
Thank you.

818
01:14:11,513 --> 01:14:18,252
(cell phone ringing)

819
01:14:18,254 --> 01:14:20,588
Yes.

820
01:14:22,458 --> 01:14:24,192
Mona.

821
01:14:24,194 --> 01:14:25,626
Mona, where are you?

822
01:14:25,628 --> 01:14:27,929
Mona, where are you,
the police are looking for you.

823
01:14:30,332 --> 01:14:32,500
I never wanted
to kill Leila

824
01:14:32,502 --> 01:14:34,535
It was
an accident.

825
01:14:34,537 --> 01:14:35,770
I know, I know.

826
01:14:35,772 --> 01:14:38,306
I know, I'm the one
who wanted to kill her.

827
01:14:38,308 --> 01:14:40,374
Please come back,
Mona, okay?

828
01:14:40,376 --> 01:14:41,576
I post
the bail for you.

829
01:14:41,578 --> 01:14:43,444
You won't go in jail.

830
01:14:43,446 --> 01:14:46,147
I'm not afraid to go
to jail, Mourad.

831
01:14:46,149 --> 01:14:47,715
<i>I'm selling the store.</i>

832
01:14:47,717 --> 01:14:49,217
We'll leave
Chicago.

833
01:14:49,219 --> 01:14:52,820
And we can
adopt children.

834
01:14:52,822 --> 01:14:55,990
We should have done
that before.

835
01:14:55,992 --> 01:14:58,459
I'm not gonna
go back to you, Mourad

836
01:14:58,461 --> 01:15:00,728
Why, why, Mona?

837
01:15:00,730 --> 01:15:02,663
I don't care
about children, okay?

838
01:15:02,665 --> 01:15:04,532
I don't care.

839
01:15:04,534 --> 01:15:06,033
She ruin her life
with this.

840
01:15:06,035 --> 01:15:09,637
Maybe I'm the one
who can't have them.

841
01:15:09,639 --> 01:15:11,739
I never had the courage
to tell her.

842
01:15:11,741 --> 01:15:14,709
And I didn't
stand up for you enough.

843
01:15:14,711 --> 01:15:16,677
<i>No, you did, I--</i>

844
01:15:16,679 --> 01:15:20,748
I loved you,
I loved you.

845
01:15:20,750 --> 01:15:24,585
So, so, so let's try again,
okay, somewhere else?

846
01:15:24,587 --> 01:15:26,654
You and me, okay?

847
01:15:26,656 --> 01:15:29,490
No Mourad,
it's over.

848
01:15:29,492 --> 01:15:33,594
We cannot build a new life
over your mother's death?

849
01:15:33,596 --> 01:15:34,829
<i>Why?</i>

850
01:15:34,831 --> 01:15:37,999
Anyway, I'm coming back
to Chicago.

851
01:15:38,001 --> 01:15:40,268
I'm gonna turn
myself in, just...

852
01:15:40,270 --> 01:15:41,969
inform the police.

853
01:15:41,971 --> 01:15:44,539
<i>No, Mona, don't do that,</i>
<i>don't do that, okay, let--</i>

854
01:15:44,541 --> 01:15:45,606
(phone disconnects)

855
01:15:45,608 --> 01:15:48,476
Mona!

856
01:15:48,478 --> 01:15:49,877
Oh.

857
01:16:30,185 --> 01:16:33,321
(church bell ringing)

858
01:16:42,364 --> 01:16:48,669
(music playing)

859
01:16:53,542 --> 01:16:55,743
Okay, thank you.

860
01:16:55,745 --> 01:16:58,112
Okay, O'Connor!

861
01:17:08,357 --> 01:17:09,690
(woman)
Your name please?

862
01:17:09,692 --> 01:17:10,691
O'Connor.

863
01:17:10,693 --> 01:17:12,293
And where you
from?

864
01:17:12,295 --> 01:17:13,527
Chicago.

865
01:17:13,529 --> 01:17:15,062
You have two
minutes.

866
01:17:17,666 --> 01:17:25,072
(music playing)

867
01:19:18,120 --> 01:19:20,087
This certificate is
for Marilyn.

868
01:19:20,089 --> 01:19:21,388
Okay.

869
01:19:23,091 --> 01:19:26,560
And... would you say goodbye
to her for me?

870
01:19:26,562 --> 01:19:28,295
Yes.

871
01:19:40,142 --> 01:19:45,946
♪

872
01:20:29,291 --> 01:20:31,892
Hello, Jack.
Hey.

873
01:20:31,894 --> 01:20:32,893
How you doing?

874
01:20:32,895 --> 01:20:34,061
Fine, how you doing?

875
01:20:34,063 --> 01:20:35,996
She needs a ticket
to Chicago.

876
01:20:35,998 --> 01:20:38,799
The train leaves
in three hours.

877
01:20:38,801 --> 01:20:42,002
I'll get it ready.
Okay.

878
01:20:42,004 --> 01:20:44,672
Okay, Jack's gonna
take care of you.

879
01:20:44,674 --> 01:20:45,840
Thank you
for everything.

880
01:20:45,842 --> 01:20:47,908
You're welcome.

881
01:20:53,715 --> 01:20:54,782
Take care of yourself.

882
01:20:54,784 --> 01:20:57,918
Be safe.

883
01:21:15,537 --> 01:21:21,508
♪

884
01:22:05,387 --> 01:22:07,688
Mona!

885
01:22:17,499 --> 01:22:22,236
♪

886
01:22:46,328 --> 01:22:50,965
You weren't gonna
say goodbye?

887
01:22:54,703 --> 01:22:59,707
They'll never believe the dance
they saw today was me.

888
01:22:59,709 --> 01:23:02,810
Where you going?

889
01:23:02,812 --> 01:23:06,914
Chicago.

890
01:23:06,916 --> 01:23:08,983
Then I'm going
with you.

